These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, fanta, lemonade, soy-milk, coffee
City: liverpool, london, paris, berlin, miami, venice, prague
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 4. the person traveling to prague is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person traveling to london is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is in the middle##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
 9. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
11. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person traveling to miami##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
14. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Beverage   | lemonade      | hot-chocolate      | soy-milk    | coffee    | sprite | almond-milk     | fanta     |
| City   | berlin | miami | paris | liverpool | venice   | prague | london |

