.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dressmaker, videographer, writer, librarian, musician, freelancer, paramedic
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, amaryllis, dahlia, aconite, marigold, lily
 1. the writer is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 3. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 5. the musician is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who growsmarigold is the librarian##1
 7. the videographer is the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the freelancer is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the librarian is the person who growsmarigold##1
10. the writer is between the person who growsmarigold and the videographer##2
11. the freelancer is in the middle##1
12. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
13. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
14. the paramedic is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Job   | videographer   | writer | librarian | freelancer   | paramedic | dressmaker | musician |
| Flower           | aconite | sunflower          | marigold    | tulip | dahlia     | amaryllis      | lily    |

