.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, dancing, woodworking, reading, board-games, sudoku
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, fantasy, family, comedy, sports, western, scientific
 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
11. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
12. the person watching sports movies is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Hobby   | woodworking        | filmmaking  | board-games | dancing | reading           | sudoku           | rock-climbing  |
| Movie-Genre    | superhero | comedy | scientific   | family    | sports | western | fantasy |

