 6. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 9. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the rat is between the person who likes mauve and the owner of the chinchilla##2
11. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
12. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| Pet   | dog     | chinchilla   | rat      | hedgehog | rabbit    | hamster | snake |
| Color       | white | green | red | mauve  | lilac | ebony     | orange    |

