.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
House: modern, wooden, townhouse, art-deco, farmhouse, ranch-style, cottage
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, rugby, badminton, basketball, surfing, biathlon, water-polo
 1. the wooden house is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 2. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is the cottage house##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is the ranch-style house##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
 7. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
 8. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the wooden house##1
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
12. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
13. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the modern house##1
14. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3

