.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
7 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, snooker, poker, backgammon, billiard, go
There are 7 different favourite colors: pink, black, purple, blue, chestnut, yellow, emerald
 1. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
 2. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
 4. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing poker is the person who likes black##1
 6. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
10. the person playing go is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
11. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
12. the person who likes black is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Game          | billiard   | snooker | go | domino | backgammon | mah-jongg | poker |
| Color   | chestnut | emerald      | yellow     | purple  | blue | pink         | black    |

 